1. Droping the table

    DROP TBAP_ITEM;

2. Dropping Column
    
    1. Dropping Single Column: 
        
            ALTER TABLE <TABLE NAME>
            DROP COLUMN <COLUMN NAME>;
            
                    OR
                    
            ALTER TABLE <TABLE NAME>
            DROP ();
    
    2. Dropping multiple columns
            
            ALTER TABLE <TABLE NAME>
            DROP (COL1, COL2);
            
            
    
            ALTER TABLE TBAP_ITEM
            DROP (AP_ID, MAIN_ITEM_ID);
    
    
